										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="SFXTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[MD] The player is pushed against the tree. They kiss. Halsin goes down on the player. We cut to a wideshot where we see a squirrel run by. Cutting back to the action, Halsin gets back to his feet and kisses the player on the neck. They fall to the ground and the romance continues on the ground" />
